name: napari-subboxer
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "napari-subboxer" %}
{% set version = "0.0.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/napari-subboxer-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 381a9e95c505e9d2240428287876ac45bb656566071b48f51e2d1f13fa2c2088

build:
  entry_points:
    - napari-subboxer = napari_subboxer.cli:cli
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.7
    - setuptools-scm
  run:
    - einops
    - eulerangles
    - mrcfile
    - napari ==0.4.12
    - napari-plugin-engine >=0.1.4
    - numpy
    - pydantic
    - python >=3.7
    - starfile
    - typer

test:
  imports:
    - napari_subboxer
  commands:
    - pip list
    - pip check
    - napari-subboxer --help
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/alisterburt/napari-subboxer
  summary: A napari plugin for interacting with electron cryotomograms
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - alisterburt
    - goanpeca
    - jaimergp
